snippet.title: Racine - Teaser
snippet.description:
First teaser of the upcoming Game Racine.

"Take your cards wanderer. The spirits are rampaging through the land and you need to find the source of their anger. Haste thyself, for time is of the essence. You’ll have to mix swiftness and care in this real time card game that will have you face waves of ferocious enemies."

Wishlist now on Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1793170/Racine/?fbclid=IwAR3nS1BW4yqP5Ft7HRlevwsBKOombNYrsaykVk5JKc3YJX8bkwBFEewDYQU

Follow us to get the latest news about the game!
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RacineGame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/racinegame/?hl=fr
